                  <formatted-text>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>📦 </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Strategic E-Commerce Analytics via Google Cloud BigQuery &amp; Modern Data Stack</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Transforms fragmented Brazilian e-commerce transaction logs into a high-performance </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>Star Schema</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'> for executive reporting. By automating the end-to-end flow from raw data to BI, we eliminated 100% of manual data preparation, providing a &quot;Single Source of Truth&quot; for Olist’s 9+ disparate datasets.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>🛠️ Methodology: The Medallion Architecture</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Implemented a modular </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>ELT (Extract, Load, Transform)</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> pipeline centered on data reliability and scalability:</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Ingestion (Bronze):</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> Automated raw data extraction via </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Meltano</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> into </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Google BigQuery</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>, preserving full data lineage.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Transformation (Silver &amp; Gold):</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> Fact/Dimension models, leveraged </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>dbt</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> to normalize schemas, standardize timestamps, and enforce </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>79+ automated data quality tests</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Analytics (Rose):</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> Developed denormalized </run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Data Marts</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'> optimized for low-latency querying and executive-level visualization.</run>
